## 🌟 Three-Tier Architecture Examples

### Example 1: Built-in Scenario (Tier 1 Match)

```yaml
User Query: "服务器很慢"

Tier 1: SKILL.md
  ├─ Extract keywords: [慢]
  ├─ Match scenario: "系统慢/卡" ✅
  ├─ Select reference: resource-saturation.md
  └─ Mode: quick → (auto) deep if abnormal

Execution:
  1. Quick scan (10s): Memory WARNING detected
  2. Auto Deep (25s): MySQL memory leak identified
  3. Report: Root cause + fixes

Result: ✅ Problem solved in 35 seconds
Tier 2/3: Not needed
```

---

### Example 2: Extended Scenario (Tier 2 Match)

```yaml
User Query: "Docker container keeps restarting"

Tier 1: SKILL.md
  ├─ Extract keywords: [Docker, restarting]
  ├─ Match scenario: None ❌
  └─ Fallback to Tier 2

Tier 2: 00-scenario-index.md
  ├─ Read: references/00-scenario-index.md
  ├─ Search: "Docker" keyword
  ├─ Match found: Category "Container Issues" ✅
  └─ Recommended actions:
      • Reference: system-logs.md --mode deep --focus crash
      • Command: commands/debugging/diagnose-crash.md

Execution:
  1. Read system-logs.md
  2. Deep crash analysis (20s)
  3. Found: OOM kills in docker logs
  4. Recommend: Increase container memory limit

Result: ✅ Problem solved in 25 seconds
```

---

### Example 3: No Match - Fallback (Tier 3)

```yaml
User Query: "How to optimize PostgreSQL performance?"

Tier 1: SKILL.md
  ├─ Extract keywords: [optimize, PostgreSQL, performance]
  ├─ Match scenario: None ❌
  └─ Fallback to Tier 2

Tier 2: 00-scenario-index.md
  ├─ Read: references/00-scenario-index.md
  ├─ Search: "PostgreSQL" keyword
  ├─ Match found: Partial ⚠️
  └─ Recommended: Database performance tuning (not in diagnostics scope)

Tier 3: Fallback Strategy
  ├─ Inform: "Database optimization is not covered in diagnostics library"
  ├─ Offer: "I can run basic health checks to identify bottlenecks"
  └─ Execute: resource-saturation.md quick mode
      Result: CPU OK, Memory WARNING (PostgreSQL using 6GB)
      Suggestion: "PostgreSQL may need query optimization or indexing"

Result: ⚠️ Limited help, but basic diagnostics provided
```

---

### Example 4: Quick Reference Optimization (Optional)

```yaml
User Query: "快速检查系统状态"

Tier 0 (Optional): 00-quick-reference.md
  ├─ Use case: AI wants < 3 second decision
  ├─ Read: references/00-quick-reference.md (187 lines vs 800+ in SKILL.md)
  ├─ Match: Scenario #7 (健康检查) ✅
  ├─ Quick decision: Run 3 Quick scans
  └─ Commands:
      • bash references/resource-saturation.md --mode quick
      • bash references/system-logs.md --mode quick
      • bash references/disk-smart.md --mode quick

Execution:
  1. Parallel Quick scans (10s total)
  2. All OK ✅
  3. Report: "系统健康，无异常"

Result: ✅ Fast decision + fast execution
```

