## 🎓 AI Learning Path

**For AI agents using this skill**:

### Phase 1: Master Tier 1 (Week 1)
- Memorize 14 built-in scenarios
- Practice Quick → Deep workflow
- Understand root cause inference templates

### Phase 2: Utilize Tier 2 (Week 2)
- Learn to query 00-scenario-index.md effectively
- Understand Commands vs References distinction
- Practice fallback strategies

### Phase 3: Optimization (Week 3)
- Use 00-quick-reference.md for speed
- Batch similar checks (health scan)
- Combine related diagnostics (disk slow = resource + SMART)

### Phase 4: Expert (Week 4+)
- Predict scenarios before matching
- Proactive Deep (no user prompt for WARNING + troubleshoot)
- Multi-component root cause correlation
